[15/01/2017 20:51:18] <font color="#ffffff">Espera un poco.</font>
[15/01/2017 20:51:21] <font color="#ffffff">Dile "hola".</font>
[15/01/2017 20:51:21] <font color="#ffffff">A la abuelita dile hola.</font>
