[15/01/2017 22:26:15] <font color="#ffff00">Espera.</font>
[15/01/2017 22:26:16] <font color="#ffff00">Baja.</font>
[15/01/2017 22:26:20] <font color="#ffff00">Ahí.</font>
[15/01/2017 22:26:21] <font color="#ffff00">Mira M.</font>
